 from us."],[3912,4062,"Logan, freeze our accounts."],[4079,4254,"Nothing comes out without my okay."],[4254,4396,"Effective immediately."],[4396,4533,"Henry, how dare you."],[4579,4813,"Daddy, why can't you help me?"],[4850,5050,"Mommy really needs your help."],[5050,5155,"Don't you dare"],[5155,5292,"bring up your mother again."],[5292,5492,"She made you beg for food"],[5492,5622,"on the streets."],[5643,5747,"That is not love."],[5809,5897,"That is cruelty."],[5976,6181,"She doesn't deserve someone like you."],[6181,6260,"From now on,"],[6373,6477,"you are my daughter."],[6573,6715,"Your mother is dead to us."]],"31":[[12,145,"No, don't say that."],[145,254,"Mommy's not bad."],[254,483,"Mommy loves me so much."],[538,621,"Shh."],[688,738,"No."],[838,996,"Sweetheart, come here."],[1026,1113,"Shh."],[1167,1259,"Look what you did"],[1259,1430,"to my precious granddaughter."],[1472,1551,"Cool off."],[1639,1710,"Out!"],[2068,2143,"Grandpa,"],[2168,2318,"Daddy hates Mommy, right?"],[2348,2544,"That's why he never came back for us."],[2573,2702,"Oh, no."],[2719,2961,"Anna, now you listen to Grandpa."],[2986,3224,"Your Daddy does not hate Mom."],[3311,3486,"In fact, it's just the opposite."],[3528,3707,"He loves her so much,"],[3732,3862,"he doesn't know"],[3862,4087,"what to do now that she's back."],[4479,4704,"Christy, how could you be so heartless?"],[4704,4942,"You're not getting anything from me."]],"32":[[2181,2281,"Oh, come on."],[2281,2369,"Not you, too."],[2477,2581,"Christy Lane,"],[2610,2727,"the violin prodigy."],[2761,2877,"Every guy who hears her play"],[2877,3007,"ends up asking her out."],[3541,3595,"Hi."],[4079,4154,"Henry Cole."],[4587,4662,"Christy Lane."],[4959,5013,"Hi."],[5764,5822,"Oh, yeah."],[5876,5943,"Let's go."],[7111,7165,"Shit!"],[8254,8324,"Christy."],[8416,8571,"You goddamn coward!"]],"33":[[604,717,"Please leave your message"],[717,796,"after the tone."],[909,992,"You wanted money,"],[1055,1109,"right?"],[1205,1309,"Well, I have it now."